[8] Funding
Date: 9 Sep 2014
From: Deb Hensley <Deborah.Hensley@flhealth.gov>


Credit from World Bank?
-----------------------
It appears to me there may be an opportunity here to "rapidly" deploy field hospitals and, to offset a small portion of our national debt. Why not deploy 2/3rds of our Federal Medical Stations to the most needed locations and request "credit" from the World Bank or our creditors for providing international aid to this global disaster? How would one push this idea forward for vetting?

